## Hardware Disclaimer

This software is designed specifically for:
- ESP32-2432S028 (Cheap Yellow Display 2.8")
- ESP32-2432S032 (Cheap Yellow Display 3.2") 
- Compatible CYD variants with ILI9341 display driver

Use with other hardware configurations is at your own risk. The developers are not responsible for any damage to hardware resulting from incorrect usage or incompatible configurations.

